    "form_header_text": "Rep. Teresa Leger Fern\u00e1ndez (NM-03) FY27 Appropriations Request (Program/Lang)",
    "form_instructions_text": "Congresswoman Teresa Leger Fern\u00e1ndez strives to ensure that the federal government invests in the programs and policies that create opportunities for New Mexico's 3rd Congressional District and our nation. She welcomes constituents and advocacy groups to submit for consideration any programmatic or language requests they deem a priority for Fiscal Year 2027. This application form is ONLY for Programmatic and Language Requests. If you are interesting in submitting a community project funding request, please visit our website at https://fernandez.house.gov/approps and scroll towards the bottom of the page to find the appropriate application. The deadline to apply for all requests is March 9.",
